Description: This  lens system is in a cusp configuration, meaning that the source lies just within one of the four cusps of the asteroid caustic of the lens. Either a mass centroid offset from the light center or a large shear is required to match the curvature of the big arc. We found the amount of external shear to be 0.11 plus or minus 0.01.
Name: SL2S J021737-051329
